titles.title: A resolution authorizing the printing of tributes and other related materials in honor of the late Senator Janet Kay Hagan.
A resolution authorizing the printing of tributes and other related materials in honor of the late Senator Janet Kay Hagan.

vote.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Unanimous Consent.

bill.summary: This resolution authorizes the printing as a Senate document of a compilation of tributes and other related materials concerning the Honorable Janet Kay Hagan, late a Senator from North Carolina.
